{"word":"ζάμενζε","slug":"ζάμενζε","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n46126\" key=\"za/menze\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ζᾰ´μεν-ζε</orth>, inseparable Suffix, denoting <sense id=\"n46126.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">motion towards</tr_>:—prop. representing <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">-σδε</foreign>, as in <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Ἀθήναζε, Θήβαζε, θύραζε</foreign> for <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Ἀθήνασδε, Θήβασδε, θύρασδε</foreign>: but sts. found with sg. Nouns, as <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἔραζε, χαμᾶζε, Ὀλυμπίαζε, Μουνυχίαζε</foreign>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0082.tlg002:194:18\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.D.\">A.D.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adv.\">Adv.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">194.18</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}